---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Projects — Aaghran Ghosh" description="A decade of building — from DevOps and full-stack development to AI products at enterprise scale and side projects I ship and run myself.">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">

    <!-- Narrative intro -->
    <p class="text-[10px] text-ink-muted tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-6">Journey</p>
    <p class="text-lg text-ink-muted leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-4">
      Started tinkering with PC builds and web projects in college. Moved into AWS, DevOps,
      and full-stack development at Via.com. Crossed into product at ZipGo, SIXT, Hevo,
      and ThoughtSpot. Now building AI products at enterprise scale — and shipping my own on the side.
    </p>
    <a href="/work" class="text-sm text-accent font-bold hover:underline">Full work history →</a>

    <!-- Section 1: Day Job -->
    <div class="border-t border-line pt-16 mt-16">
      <p class="text-[10px] text-ink-muted tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-1">Day job</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-ink-muted mb-10">What I do full-time.</p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-start">
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 flex-wrap mb-4">
            <div>
              <p class="text-[10px] text-ink-muted mb-3 tracking-wide">Enterprise AI · Principal PM</p>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-ink tracking-tightest mb-4">Spotter @ ThoughtSpot</h2>
            </div>
            <span class="text-[10px] bg-ink text-canvas px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full font-semibold whitespace-nowrap self-start mt-1">
              ● Live · Enterprise
            </span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">
            Natural language search and agentic analytics for enterprises — letting users ask questions
            of their data in plain English and get governed, trustworthy answers. I'm on the Spotter
            product team focused on the core agent experience and customization via Spotter Analysts.
          </p>
          <a href="https://www.thoughtspot.com/product/agents/spotter" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"
            class="text-sm text-accent font-bold hover:underline">
            See Spotter →
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-line">
          <video
            src="https://media.thoughtspot.com/35707/1769749943-spotter_3-promo.mp4"
            autoplay muted loop playsinline
            class="w-full h-auto"
          ></video>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 2: Side Builds -->
    <div class="border-t border-line pt-16 mt-16">
      <p class="text-[10px] text-ink-muted tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-1">Side builds</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-ink-muted mb-10">Things I built and run myself.</p>

      <!-- WanderingBong -->
      <div class="pb-12 border-b border-line mb-12">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-start">
          <div>
            <p class="text-[10px] text-ink-muted mb-3 tracking-wide">Travel blog · MCP-connected</p>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-ink tracking-tightest mb-4">WanderingBong</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">
              A slow-travel blog I've run since 2015 — through WordPress, Strapi, and eventually
              a backend I built myself. Now MCP-connected: agents handle tags, linking, SEO, and
              metadata. I show up with the experience. They handle everything around it.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-5">
              {['MCP', 'Claude API', 'Node.js', 'Supabase'].map(t => (
                <span class="text-[10px] bg-accent-subtle border border-accent-ring text-accent px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">{t}</span>
              ))}
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-5">
              <a href="https://wanderingbong.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="text-sm text-accent font-bold hover:underline">Live blog →</a>
              <a href="/projects/wanderingbong" class="text-sm text-ink-muted hover:text-ink transition-colors">Full story →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a href="https://wanderingbong.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"
            class="block rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-line hover:border-accent transition-colors">
            <img
              src="https://d2ix4gkka8i61y.cloudfront.net/1c5b982c-eb2e-4837-b59c-7c7f49283240/images/2026/01/2ddb957aef680d67c692e965e7648c6df39ad9554c8f231c3a38005f8a2a93bb-medium.jpeg"
              alt="WanderingBong"
              class="w-full h-48 object-cover"
            />
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Roami -->
      <div class="pb-12 border-b border-line mb-12">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-start">
          <div>
            <p class="text-[10px] text-ink-muted mb-3 tracking-wide">Travel app · React Native</p>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-ink tracking-tightest mb-4">Roami</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">
              A travel journaling app built to replace the Notes-app chaos of actual travel.
              Dark editorial design, Supabase backend, self-tested on a multi-island trip in Thailand.
              The productized version of the WanderingBong pipeline — for anyone, not just me.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-5">
              {['React Native', 'Expo', 'Supabase', 'TypeScript'].map(t => (
                <span class="text-[10px] bg-accent-subtle border border-accent-ring text-accent px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">{t}</span>
              ))}
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-5">
              <a href="https://roami.xyz" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="text-sm text-accent font-bold hover:underline">roami.xyz →</a>
              <a href="/projects/roami" class="text-sm text-ink-muted hover:text-ink transition-colors">Full story →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl bg-surface border border-line p-6 flex items-center justify-center min-h-[12rem]">
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="text-2xl font-black text-ink tracking-tightest mb-2">Roami</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-ink-muted">Travel journaling, without the friction.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Lyaadh -->
      <div>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-start">
          <div>
            <p class="text-[10px] text-ink-muted mb-3 tracking-wide">Brand · Lifestyle</p>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-ink tracking-tightest mb-4">Lyaadh</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">
              Bengali for the art of pleasurable lethargy. A brand built around doing less, better —
              ShortCuts (a task shrinker with a Coma Mode), Dokan (curated gear for doing nothing),
              and slow travel. Tagline: The Art of Productive Laziness.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-5">
              {['Next.js', 'Supabase', 'Tailwind'].map(t => (
                <span class="text-[10px] bg-accent-subtle border border-accent-ring text-accent px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">{t}</span>
              ))}
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-5">
              <a href="https://lyaadh.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="text-sm text-accent font-bold hover:underline">lyaadh.com →</a>
              <a href="/projects/lyaadh" class="text-sm text-ink-muted hover:text-ink transition-colors">Full story →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl bg-surface border border-line p-6 flex items-center justify-center min-h-[12rem]">
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="text-2xl font-black text-ink tracking-tightest mb-2">Lyaadh</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-ink-muted italic">The Art of Productive Laziness.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 3: Experiments -->
    <div class="border-t border-line pt-16 mt-16">
      <p class="text-[10px] text-ink-muted tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-1">Experiments</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-ink-muted mb-10">Built to learn. Some still running.</p>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <!-- Eidetic -->
        <a href="/projects/eidetic"
          class="bg-surface border border-line rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-accent-ring transition-colors block group">
          <p class="text-[10px] text-ink-muted mb-3">Knowledge Graph · MCP</p>
          <h3 class="text-base font-black text-ink tracking-tightest mb-2 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">Eidetic</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-ink-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Chrome extension + mobile app + MCP server. Captures anything I read, makes it searchable by Claude mid-conversation.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1">
            {['MCP', 'pgvector', 'FastAPI'].map(t => (
              <span class="text-[9px] bg-accent-subtle border border-accent-ring text-accent px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-full">{t}</span>
            ))}
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- BIRD → Snowflake -->
        <a href="https://github.com/aaghran/bird-snowflake-loader" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"
          class="bg-surface border border-line rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-accent-ring transition-colors block group">
          <p class="text-[10px] text-ink-muted mb-3">NLS · Benchmarking · Open source</p>
          <h3 class="text-base font-black text-ink tracking-tightest mb-2 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">BIRD → Snowflake</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-ink-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Nobody had built a Snowflake loader for the BIRD NL-to-SQL benchmark. I needed one for evaluating Spotter, so I built it and open-sourced it.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1">
            {['Python', 'Snowflake', 'pandas'].map(t => (
              <span class="text-[9px] bg-accent-subtle border border-accent-ring text-accent px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-full">{t}</span>
            ))}
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- Worldview -->
        <a href="/projects/worldview"
          class="bg-surface border border-line rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-accent-ring transition-colors block group">
          <p class="text-[10px] text-ink-muted mb-3">Data Viz · 3D Globe</p>
          <h3 class="text-base font-black text-ink tracking-tightest mb-2 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">Worldview</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-ink-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Every tracked satellite in orbit, right now. CelesTrak TLE data, satellite.js propagation, Mapbox GL v3 globe. Scrub through time.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1">
            {['Mapbox GL', 'satellite.js', 'Three.js'].map(t => (
              <span class="text-[9px] bg-accent-subtle border border-accent-ring text-accent px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-full">{t}</span>
            ))}
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 4: Earlier Work -->
    <div class="border-t border-line pt-16 mt-16">
      <p class="text-[10px] text-ink-muted tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-1">Earlier</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-ink-muted mb-8">Where it started.</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-6">
        Before product, I was a developer. Built SEO systems and frontend tooling at Via.com —
        a Node.js + Redis content platform across 8 countries and 5 languages, driving a 200% increase
        in organic traffic. Before that, AWS, DevOps, and more PC builds than I should have spent money on.
      </p>
      <a href="/work" class="text-sm text-accent font-bold hover:underline">Full work history →</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</Layout>
